snippet.title: Hello Neighbor VR: Search and Rescue - Reveal Teaser | Meta Quest 2 + Rift S
snippet.description:
Hello Neighbor universe is coming to Oculus! Step inside your creepy Neighbor’s house, and experience it all in VR!

Hello Neighbor: Search and Rescue is a brand new groundbreaking VR horror-puzzle game where you sneak into your creepy neighbor's house to save your friend.
